{"tid":1664544,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"IELTS vs TOEFL一問","createTime":"2019-10-20T07:56:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T11:39:19.000Z","uid":80460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"3f4ac51fb40f55e79aabffd9e6611656d590da01","tid":1664544,"uid":80460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T07:56:50.000Z","msg":"講返背景，要考IELTS因為讀完某專業科要拎外國牌，佢要求IELTS大分7所有細分至少6.5或者TOEFL IBT &gt;=100/120<br />\n<br />\n以前考過IELTS幾次都係死writing，2年前成績如下<br />\n大分7.0 Writing 6 Oral 6.5 Listening 7.5 Reading 8.5<br />\n<br />\n如果想補writing同oral邊度好D?<br />\n又，TOEFL係咪相對IELTS難D?"},{"pid":"f6e619758bba6597302e2d0359103da6334cdd6f","tid":1664544,"uid":331192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T08:41:23.000Z","msg":"LM"},{"pid":"78d8054043664a952504ce8d86408a66c6ae807c","tid":1664544,"uid":80460,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T13:59:40.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bf19034acf90a6c26f2c9670725a41d4eaa2372","tid":1664544,"uid":312758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-21T11:39:19.000Z","msg":"Writing同Oral, 要改變思考方式先會好，你要代入鬼佬既思維方法。<br />\n<br />\n考到IELTS就唔好搞TOEFL啦，份卷唔啱你做。"}]}